    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Curacao</placeName>
                <date>29th November 5615 <add>1854</add></date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd. I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Your valued favor of <date>28th Septr.</date> Came duly<lb/> to
                hand—contents noted. The box of books did not arrive here<lb/> till the
                    <date>9th</date> inst:, but all in good condition, and comformable to
                Invoice<lb/> amount of which is $93„00. I shall endeavor to sell them all as
                soon<lb/> as possible. I have but two sets of the Prayer Book, former lot,
                commonest<lb/> sort, but require no more. I hold at present the sum of $55. for
                you<lb/> and shall try my best to increase it. There is a great number of<lb/> old
                Occidents on hand which I will return to you by the<lb/> next opportunity. At
                present I have not time to attend to them.<lb/> It is my intention to bid farewell
                to this <placeName>island</placeName> next <date>March</date><lb/> and shall visit
                your city with two of my brothers on our<lb/> route to
                    <placeName>Australia</placeName>. If I have any books remaining at that
                time<lb/> shall, with your permission, leave them with <persName>Mr.
                    Nathan</persName><lb/> who will do all he can for your interest.</p>
            <p>I regret that you have not sent me the two pairs of Sephilim<add>?</add><lb/> which I
                asked of you<lb/> I earnestly beg you to forward them by the<lb/> first opportunity.
                Trusting that you are enjoying health<lb/> I remain as ever Yours faithfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <persName role="author">EH Lindo</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
